[bg city_night]
[music ambient_city]
[+ Copper smile]
>Copper  
Hey, it's been a while since we walked together like this.  
[Copper mv 15]  
[Copper look right]  
Look at that... the city lights are beautiful tonight, don't you think?  

@You nod, feeling a slight chill in the air.  
[bg anim up 1]

[+ Bowden serious]
>Bowden  
You seem distracted. Is everything okay?  

@You hesitate, then decide to speak your mind.  
[choice "Yes, I'm fine", "No, something's on my mind", "Let's not talk about it"]
    [case 1]
        >Copper  
        Oh, good. For a moment, I thought you were upset with me.  
        [goto calmScene]
    [case 2]
        >Copper  
        You know you can tell us anything, right?  
        >Bowden  
        We're here for you.  
        [goto comfortScene]
    [case 3]
        >Copper  
        Alright, if that's what you want.  
        @The silence feels heavy as you all keep walking.  
        [goto quietScene]
    [end choice]

[clear]
[transition black 1000]
[bg forest_night]
[music peaceful_forest]
@The group has moved away from the city and is now deep in the forest, the moonlight filtering through the trees.  

[+ Copper]
[Copper loop smile]
>Copper  
I love it here. It's so peaceful, don't you think?  

[+ Bowden]
>Bowden  
It's quiet... too quiet.  
[Copper anim laugh]
>Bowden  
I'm serious!  

[var courage 5]
[var courage +3]
[if courage >= 8]
    >Copper  
    Wow, you're really brave to laugh in a place like this.  
[else]
    >Copper  
    I can tell you're uneasy, but it's okay. We've got your back.  
[endif]

[sound rustle]
@A sudden rustling sound breaks the silence.  
[Copper look left]
[+layer shadow 2]
>Copper  
Did you hear that?  

[choice "Investigate", "Stay still", "Run"]
    [case 1]
        >Bowden  
        Let's check it out. Be ready for anything.  
        [goto investigateScene]
    [case 2]
        @You decide to stay still, barely breathing as you listen.  
        [goto stealthScene]
    [case 3]
        >Copper  
        Running might not be the best idea, but... okay!  
        [goto escapeScene]
    [end choice]

